                            <comment id="13237071" author="hossman" created="Fri, 23 Mar 2012 20:31:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Bulk changing fixVersion 3.6 to 4.0 for any open issues that are unassigned and have not been updated since March 19.&lt;/p&gt;

